original_title: Ladies of Soul - Live At The Ziggodome 2015
overview: Concert by the Ladies of Soul at the Ziggodome Amsterdam in 2015. The Ladies of Soul consists of Trijntje Oosterhuis, Berget Lewis, Glennis Grace, Edsilia Rombley, and Candy Dulfer. Special guests include Sheila E., Chance Howard, and Re-Play.
tagline: Ladies of Soul - Live At The Ziggodome
title: Ladies of Soul - Live At The Ziggodome 2015
